+.\"TOPICS "Topics:"
+.TH MC 1 "September 2007" "MC Version 4.6.2-pre1" "GNU Midnight Commander"
+.\"SKIP_SECTION"
+.SH "NAME"
+mc \- Visual shell for Unix-like systems.
